\ncase A 冇倉 姐係冇任何貨都會搞成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好驚喎。。。用緊一通但冇玩期指 搞到想轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ae054df42c8f65398480660e9f9b00ec363579","tid":353342,"uid":41944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T10:32:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>話說我有朋友用一通<br />\n<br />\nCASE A:佢本身冇倉，無啦啦多左張期指，結果輸左4千幾，同CS EMAIL左幾輪之後 CS就唔理佢...上到分行話冇野幫到佢，然後CHECK過落單IP，話係A 自己既手機...<br />\n<br />\nCASE B: 佢炒開STOCK OPTION既，有一日在有足夠按金情況下斬左倉，輸左幾皮野，然後CS都係唔理佢，話一通有權咁做。最後威脅要嘈到上證監先肯賠...<br />\n<br />\n其實...一通個SYSTEM點解咁多問題...在職其間係咪收到好多投訴?</blockquote><br />\n所以樓主唔撚撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\ncase B 我都試過。結果第二日佢補返個倉俾我，佢應該蝕左幾千<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b913d18d866f16205f0a2cd38671cba23b95aca","tid":353342,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T10:34:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有出post呀jobsdb</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大哥我想問下而家一通有無雙糧花紅/醫療？<br />\n我記得內部試好多人肥 肥完之後仲要放工去聽老闆解返答案</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2217fdeda6081cf881fbaeaf650b1b9db5c9402","tid":353342,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T10:34:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有出po